items.title: 100 Continue
items.subtitle: Request received, continue sending the request.

items.title: 101 Switching protocols
items.subtitle: Server is switching protocols as requested.

items.title: 102 Processing
items.subtitle: Request received, processing in progress.

items.title: 103 Early Hints
items.subtitle: Provides early hints to help with preloading.

items.title: 200 OK
items.subtitle: Request succeeded, the response contains the requested data.

items.title: 201 Created
items.subtitle: Request succeeded, a new resource was created.

items.title: 202 Accepted
items.subtitle: Request accepted, processing is not yet complete.

items.title: 203 Non-Authoritative Information
items.subtitle: Returned data may be from a different source.

items.title: 204 No Content
items.subtitle: Request succeeded, but no content to send.

items.title: 205 Reset Content
items.subtitle: Request succeeded, reset the view.

items.title: 206 Partial Content
items.subtitle: Partial data is returned as requested.

items.title: 207 Multi-Status
items.subtitle: Multiple status codes for a multi-resource response.

items.title: 208 Already Reported
items.subtitle: The resource has already been reported.

items.title: 226 IM Used
items.subtitle: Response content follows instance-manipulations.

items.title: 300 Multiple Choices
items.subtitle: Multiple options for the resource are available.

items.title: 301 Moved Permanently
items.subtitle: The resource has been moved to a new URL permanently.

items.title: 302 Found (Previously "Moved Temporarily")
items.subtitle: The resource has been temporarily moved to a new URL.

items.title: 303 See Other
items.subtitle: Redirect to a different resource, usually for POST.

items.title: 304 Not Modified
items.subtitle: The resource has not been modified since the last request.

items.title: 305 Use Proxy
items.subtitle: The resource must be accessed through a proxy.

items.title: 306 Switch Proxy
items.subtitle: No longer used; reserved for future use.

items.title: 307 Temporary Redirect
items.subtitle: Temporary redirection to a new URL, method not changed.

items.title: 308 Permanent Redirect
items.subtitle: Permanent redirection to a new URL, method not changed.

items.title: 400 Bad Request
items.subtitle: The request is invalid or malformed.

items.title: 401 Unauthorized
items.subtitle: Authentication is required to access the resource.

items.title: 402 Payment Required
items.subtitle: Reserved for future use; usually related to payment.

items.title: 403 Forbidden
items.subtitle: You do not have permission to access this resource.

items.title: 404 Not Found
items.subtitle: The requested resource could not be found.

items.title: 405 Method Not Allowed
items.subtitle: The HTTP method is not allowed for the resource.

items.title: 406 Not Acceptable
items.subtitle: The requested resource is not acceptable.

items.title: 407 Proxy Authentication Required
items.subtitle: Authentication with a proxy is required.

items.title: 408 Request Timeout
items.subtitle: The request took too long to complete.

items.title: 409 Conflict
items.subtitle: The request conflicts with the current state of the resource.

items.title: 410 Gone
items.subtitle: The resource is no longer available.

items.title: 411 Length Required
items.subtitle: The request must specify the content length.

items.title: 412 Precondition Failed
items.subtitle: A precondition specified in the request failed.

items.title: 413 Payload Too Large
items.subtitle: The request entity is too large.

items.title: 414 URI Too Long
items.subtitle: The request URI is too long.

items.title: 415 Unsupported Media Type
items.subtitle: The media type is not supported.

items.title: 416 Range Not Satisfiable
items.subtitle: The requested range is not satisfiable.

items.title: 417 Expectation Failed
items.subtitle: The server cannot meet the request's expectations.

items.title: 418 I'm a Teapot
items.subtitle: Just for fun; the server is a teapot.

items.title: 419 Page Expired (Laravel)
items.subtitle: The page has expired, typically for security reasons.

items.title: 420 Page Expired (Spring Framework)
items.subtitle: The page has expired, typically for security reasons.

items.title: 421 Misdirected Request
items.subtitle: The request was directed to an incorrect server.

items.title: 422 Unprocessable Entity
items.subtitle: The request is well-formed but could not be processed.

items.title: 423 Locked
items.subtitle: The resource is locked.

items.title: 424 Failed Dependency
items.subtitle: A previous request failed, so this request cannot be fulfilled.

items.title: 425 Too Early
items.subtitle: Indicates that the server is unwilling to process the request.

items.title: 426 Upgrade Required
items.subtitle: Client must upgrade to a different protocol.

items.title: 428 Precondition Required
items.subtitle: The server requires the request to be conditional.

items.title: 429 Too Many Requests
items.subtitle: Too many requests have been sent in a given time.

items.title: 430 Request Header Fields Too Large (Shopify)
items.subtitle: The header fields are too large (specific to Shopify).

items.title: 431 Request Header Fields Too Large
items.subtitle: The request's header fields are too large.

items.title: 450 Blocked by Windows Parental Controls (Microsoft)
items.subtitle: Blocked by Windows Parental Controls.

items.title: 451 Unavailable For Legal Reasons
items.subtitle: The resource is unavailable due to legal reasons.

items.title: 500 Internal Server Error
items.subtitle: A generic server error occurred.

items.title: 501 Not Implemented
items.subtitle: The server does not support the functionality required.

items.title: 502 Bad Gateway
items.subtitle: Invalid response received from an upstream server.

items.title: 503 Service Unavailable
items.subtitle: The server is currently unavailable.

items.title: 504 Gateway Timeout
items.subtitle: The server did not receive a timely response from an upstream server.

items.title: 505 HTTP Version Not Supported
items.subtitle: The server does not support the HTTP protocol version.

items.title: 506 Variant Also Negotiates
items.subtitle: A variant of the resource leads to negotiation failures.

items.title: 507 Insufficient Storage
items.subtitle: The server is unable to store the representation needed.

items.title: 508 Loop Detected
items.subtitle: The server detected an infinite loop while processing the request.

items.title: 509 Bandwidth Limit Exceeded (Apache Web Server/cPanel)
items.subtitle: The server exceeded the bandwidth limit.

items.title: 510 Not Extended
items.subtitle: Further extensions are required to fulfill the request.

items.title: 511 Network Authentication Required
items.subtitle: Network authentication is required.
